        ‚ö†Ô∏è Mid-term exams will begin from October 10.
      </div>
      <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
        üì¢ College Fest ‚ÄúEduSpark 2025‚Äù coming soon!
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Help Content -->
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="pills-help" role="tabpanel">
      <h4>Need Help?</h4>
      <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@mycollege.edu">support@mycollege.edu</a> or call +1-234-567-890.</p>
